data.text:
The worst experience ever, we booked originally through booking.com as a package( flight and hotel) with Sunotel Aston, we paid for 7 nights but 6 nights stay since  we were on the way for the 1st night, when we arrived to the hotel, they said that they were waiting for us the night before and since nobody notify them, they canceled our reservation with no call, email or follow up with us or priceline package(through booking.com), they said we will do a favour to you for not letting you stay at the street tonight! And how ever you had already paid for your hotel, we will charge you for another hotel” Sunotel Junior” and you should come back tomorrow and talk to the manager; 
We paid double price for the cheaper quality Sunotel Junior hotel with the dirty small room, we could not even open the door of washroom because of awfull smell and not ventilated. No safety box, 
When client book a package, the 3rd party( agancy or,…) need to be in contact with other providers or the hotel should have some follow up when working in partnership with other agents/websits,….the next day, they reimbursed us the our 1st night with no price difference because of lower quality, so we went back to Sunotel Aston but all of those were such a headache after 19 hrs flight from Vancouver-Canada and above all of that they were not understanding and their treatment was so rude…..
